snippet.title: Arcturus - The Curse and Loss of Divinity - Opening Movie
snippet.description:
Arcturus-The Curse and Loss of Divinity
is a korean RPG for PC made by Sonnori & Gravity.
Original name: 악튜러스
It was later translated to Japanese and published for the Japan market by Falcom
